Dallas Cowboys at New Orleans Saints

headlines.description: — Dallas defensive coordinator Dan Quinn had to step in for Mike McCarthy as acting head coach and enjoyed the sideline view as the unit he normally oversees lifted the Cowboys out of their recent swoon with a slew of big plays.
headlines.shortLinkText: Defense lifts Dallas to 27-17 victory over sinking Saints
